snippet.title: Raiden IV x MIKADO remix Trailer
snippet.description:
THE ROAR OF THUNDER IS BACK! 
The series that changed the history of arcade shoot'em ups is coming to Nintendo Switch. 
Instill fear in your enemies with devastating attacks and earn the acclaimed title of Master Ace!
